{"tid":726430,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"同女朋友搵野食真係好頭痕","createTime":"2018-07-02T11:31:26.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-05T13:37:35.000Z","uid":137335,"like":36,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"2ce1a7d61d8d603fda9b46ce83bc101504088d3b","tid":726430,"uid":137335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T11:31:26.000Z","msg":"又叫你諗 講比佢又呢樣熱氣果樣怕肥<br />\n<br />\n於是小弟決定將呢樣野交比program拆掂佢<br />\n<br />\n細佬寫咗簡單既program去random抽一間餐廳出黎<br />\n<br />\n先加咗想食果堆餐廳，跟住再咁一間食乜就會出random既ans<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/02/192848_cc61f32295eb0de2f9988581bfb9bbd2.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F02%2F192848_cc61f32295eb0de2f9988581bfb9bbd2.jpeg&h=d76f0a2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n個app零廣告 零權限<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/02/192837_a1a3f319c27f2e900bcd69a9ad4459dc.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F02%2F192837_a1a3f319c27f2e900bcd69a9ad4459dc.jpeg&h=b735a914&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n純粹自娛之後公諸同好，所以連Google play都冇上架<br />\n<br />\n淨係用過自己機test過，有機會有bug<br />\n<br />\n只限android<br />\napk: <a href=\"https://drive.google.com/open?id=1xpkTmWxdOcgJJ6y2f2tVOVYzIFPlHfxy\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Fopen%3Fid%3D1xpkTmWxdOcgJJ6y2f2tVOVYzIFPlHfxy&d=nbPBpL95CC5kiLBe3I2%2Fd9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=b0859d2f\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/open?id=1xpkTmWxdOcgJJ6y2f2tVOVYzIFPlHfxy</a>"},{"pid":"9fcdfbaa1fa7786479c34b136a924fcdeece3fab","tid":726430,"uid":137703,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T11:48:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"451df57e5c5d7567a1740661d3df74536f152489","tid":726430,"uid":177152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T11:49:43.000Z","msg":"概念幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gi